text: I then worked as a Software Engineer at Klarna Bank AB, Sweden, from May 2023 to May 2024. topic: Experience - Senior Software Engineer at Klarna Bank AB
text: Currently, I am a Senior Software Engineer at Klarna Bank AB, Sweden, since January 2024. I am responsible for centralizing the organization’s internal data, designing ETL pipelines, creating data models, and collaborating with teams to align integration requirements for data migration.

My first experience was as an R&D Engineer at Novel-Ti, Tunisia, from September 2018 to July 2021, where I worked on several advanced AI and computer vision projects. These included developing a Deep Learning OCR system, a Real-Time Goal Line Detection System, autonomous robot navigation algorithms, body parts detection models for video games aimed at children with special needs, and a comprehensive text analysis system.

My technical skills include:

topic: Experience - IT Consultant & Machine Learning Engineer at Aigometri AB
text: I then worked as an IT Consultant and Machine Learning Engineer at Aigometri AB, Sweden, from August 2021 to April 2022. During this time, I contributed to automating client businesses, setting up ETL pipelines, testing and recommending ML algorithms, and developing a system for storing employment requests.

topic: Experience - Data Engineer at Klarna Bank AB
text: My following experience was a Data Engineer at Klarna Bank AB, Sweden, from May 2022 to May 2023. In this role, I designed and built data pipelines, redesigned ETL processes for better performance, managed third-party integrations, and developed interactive dashboards to support executive decision-making.

I am an experienced software engineer specializing in AI, machine learning, and data engineering. My career spans various roles where I have developed AI solutions, built data pipelines, and created LLM-based systems. I am passionate about leveraging advanced technologies to drive innovation and solve real-world problems, with a well-rounded skill set.
